# ChangeLog for x11-base/x11-drm
# Copyright 1999-2006 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: $

  01 May 2008; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Define GIT_REVISION in make, thanks to Olivier Huber.
  Gives the proper version info in kernel log when nouveau.ko loaded.

  19 Apr 2008; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Add Marcheu's hack as a patch to implement __ucmpdi2 on ppc32.

  16 Feb 2008; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Patch by Peter Hjalmarsson (xake):
  Updates from official Portage, excluding building of libdrm and
  dristat, drmstat. Patches moved to files/patch/.

  06 Nov 2007; Maarten Maathuis <madman2003@gmail.com> :
  Set EGIT_REPO_URI after inheriting the git eclass.

  14 Oct 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Use pkg_postinst from linux-mod.eclass, enables module-rebuild
  to work with this package. Thanks to Pierre Lejeune.

  08 Jul 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Removed useless cruft from ebuild and also references to kernel 2.4
  support; 2.4 is not supported by upstream.

  08 May 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Remove -* from KEYWORDS.

  06 Apr 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Do not compile libdrm, as it is not installed by this ebuild.
  Commented out some unused variables and old messages.

  06 Apr 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  'install' make target has appeared in upstream Makefile;
  rename our install target as 'install_for_gentoo'.

  21 Dec 2006; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  The nouveau-1 git branch for DRM has been merged to master branch.
  Switch to master branch.

*x11-drm-99999999 (30 Nov 2006)

  30 Nov 2006; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  I am picking up ebuild maintenance. Fixed the problem with
  getting git-src updated. Fix kernel version checks (QA).
